OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FTens of thousands are set to take to
OL,8,Fthe streets across Northern Ireland
OL,9,Ffor the Orange Order's annual July 12
OL,10,Fparades.
OL,12,FThe festivities will be spread across
OL,13,F18 main locations on Monday to mark
OL,14,Fthe 336th anniversary of the Battle of
OL,15,Fthe Boyne where the Protestant King
OL,16,FWilliam of Orange triumphed over the
OL,17,FCatholic King James II.
OL,19,FOrangemen and women from more than
OL,20,F1,000 lodges will be accompanied by
OL,21,Faround 600 marching bands.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
