PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784054884
OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FThe County Armagh demonstration is
OL,8,Fgenerally regarded as the largest
OL,9,Fparade while Belfast has the longest
OL,10,FTwelfth parade route of the day, with
OL,11,Fparticipants walking more than six
OL,12,Fmiles to the field.
OL,14,FThe celebrations come after the
OL,15,Fburning of bonfires at hundreds of
OL,16,Flocations in loyalist neighbourhoods
OL,17,Facross the region on Friday, Saturday
OL,18,Fand Sunday nights.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
