PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784054884
OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FAs July 12 fell on a Sunday this year,
OL,8,Fthe main Twelfth parades are instead
OL,9,Ftaking place on Monday July 13, with
OL,10,Fthe forecast predicting warm and sunny
OL,11,Fweather.
OL,13,FThe Orange Order parade in Rossnowlagh
OL,14,Fin Co Donegal took place on Saturday.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, the traditional July 13
OL,17,Fevents organised by the Royal Black
OL,18,FPreceptory in the village of Scarva,
OL,19,FCo Armagh, will instead take place on
OL,20,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
