OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784054884
OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FThe event includes a parade as well as
OL,8,Fa sham fight between actors playing
OL,9,Frival monarchs William and James.
OL,11,FWhile most of the bonfires which were
OL,12,Fburnt in recent nights were
OL,13,Funcontentious, there was condemnation
OL,14,Fafter a replica of a mosque was placed
OL,15,Fon top of a bonfire in Moyghashel, Co
OL,16,FTyrone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
