OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FThe fire was lit earlier than
OL,8,Fanticipated on Thursday after the
OL,9,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,10,F(PSNI) commenced an operation to
OL,11,Fremove the effigy.
OL,13,FA man died in hospital in Saturday
OL,14,Fafter falling off a loyalist bonfire
OL,15,Fin east Belfast on Friday night.
OL,17,FAnd in Greenisland, a fire which
OL,18,Fdestroyed two houses in was most
OL,19,Flikely caused by embers from a nearby
OL,20,Fbonfire, the fire service said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
