OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FMain Orange Order parades will take
OL,8,Fplace on Monday in Ballymena, Larne,
OL,9,FBallymoney, Portglenone, Glenarm,
OL,10,FNewtownhamilton, Belfast, Rathfriland,
OL,11,FKillyleagh, Royal Hillsborough,
OL,12,FBallymartin, Ballywalter,
OL,13,FMaguiresbridge, Limavady, Kilrea,
OL,14,FCookstown, Castlederg and Aughnacloy.
OL,16,FThe PSNI will undertake one of its
OL,17,Fbiggest policing operations of the
OL,18,Fyear on Monday to facilitate the
OL,19,Fparades.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
