OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,FOrange Order Grand Master Harold
OL,8,FHenning said the significance of
OL,9,FOrange culture and tradition is
OL,10,F"underlined by the scale of the
OL,11,Fparades".
OL,13,FHe said: "The tradition of Orange
OL,14,Fparades stretch back 230 years, and
OL,15,Fthe Twelfth continues to draw huge
OL,16,Fattendances of both participants and
OL,17,Fspectators.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@HO]uD@JOU
