PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784054884
OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,F"Our parades are a vibrant public
OL,8,Fexpression of our identity, culture
OL,9,Fand heritage and that tradition is one
OL,10,Fwhich is held dear by a great many
OL,11,Fpeople in our community."
OL,13,FHe added: "The colour and pageantry on
OL,14,Fshow on the Twelfth has increasingly
OL,15,Fbeen proven to be an attraction to
OL,16,Fvisitors to Northern Ireland seeking
OL,17,Fan authentic cultural and heritage
OL,18,Fexperience.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@YO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
