CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784054884
OL,3,CTens of thousands set to take to
OL,4,Cstreets for Twelfth Orange Order
OL,5,Cparades
OL,7,F"The hundreds of bands on display
OL,8,Finclude some of the very best marching
OL,9,Fflute, pipe, brass and accordion bands
OL,10,Fin the world. The iconic traditional
OL,11,Fsound of the Lambeg drum is another
OL,12,Funique aspect of the Twelfth, and one
OL,13,Fwhich we are glad to see flourishing
OL,14,Fwith a new generation of fifers and
OL,15,Fdrummers."
